# DBCA Global Website - Project Rules & Context

## Project Overview

DBCA Global (dbcaglobal.com) is a U.S.-based procurement and logistics consultancy website. Static HTML site optimized for AI-assisted maintenance.

**Company:** DBCA Global, LLC  
**Location:** Austin, TX  
**Target Audience:** International vendors, U.S. manufacturers, logistics partners

## Architecture

### Technology Stack
- **Static HTML5** - No framework
- **CSS** - custom.css (overrides) + main.css (theme base)
- **Font:** Open Sans (Google Fonts, weights: 300, 400, 600, 700)
- **Dev Server:** `serve` package (port 3010)
- **Deployment:** Cloudflare Pages

### File Structure
```
/
├── index.html              # Homepage
├── about/index.html        # Company & founder
├── services/index.html     # Service offerings
├── why-dbca/index.html     # Value proposition
├── contact/index.html      # Contact info
├── assets/
│   ├── css/
│   │   ├── custom.css     # All custom styles
│   │   ├── main.css       # Theme base (HTML5 UP Aerial)
│   │   └── noscript.css   # Non-JS fallback
│   ├── logo.svg
│   └── logo.png
├── docs/                   # Private (gitignored)
├── _redirects             # Cloudflare URL routing
└── _headers               # Security headers
```

### Clean URLs
- Directory-based: `/about` → `/about/index.html`
- Configured via `_redirects` with 200 rewrites

